==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: dibs
<hw>dibs</hw> <pr>(d⟦icr⟧bz)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A
sweet preparation or treacle of grape juice, much used in the
East.</def> <rj><au>Johnston.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A small amount of money.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>A right or claim, such as the right of use, or of
first choice; <as>as, I have <ex>dibs</ex> on the binoculars after Jim
is finished.</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>dibstone</ent>⟦br⟧
